{"tid":1394312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人發現tvb新聞從來都唔提連儂牆呢個名詞？","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:34:03.000Z","uid":66260,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e84e42d8ec9308185bfc0d300986a9e175d2d9d","tid":1394312,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"當now新聞，有線新聞，甚至文匯大公都叫連儂牆<br />\ncctvb硬係要叫&ldquo;寫上訴求既紙張&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知點解tvb唔俾叫連儂牆？"},{"pid":"a5d241702839b6308ed7389500cc5c833d967eee","tid":1394312,"uid":132686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"我記得好似係有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知有冇記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58d68ceccc1636e8f5f2cd6d1d3a04f37917638","tid":1394312,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:19:11.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"ef9436a133e612015f0ef874e970c700e85f6b80","tid":1394312,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"有介紹過出處<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/internationalnewsfile/5d311374e60383a20ffff061/%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Finternationalnewsfile%2F5d311374e60383a20ffff061%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIETbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=dac024e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/internationalnewsfile/5d311374e60383a20ffff061/%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86</a><br />\n連儂牆 2019-07-19 11:00 <br />\n<br />\n近期本港多區公眾地方都有市民貼上便利貼，表達反修訂《逃犯條例》等訴求；而在2014年佔領運動期間，亦有人在金鐘夏慤道張貼紙條表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n1980年12月8日，英國樂隊披頭四成員約翰連儂在紐約寓所外被歌迷槍殺身亡，而他與太太1971年創作的《Imagine》，被視為宣揚愛與和平的經典金曲。<br />\n<br />\n1988年，捷克首都布拉格有民眾在修道院廣場的一道牆上，寫上標語及塗鴉，表達對胡薩克共產政權的不滿。部分人在牆上畫有約翰連儂的肖像，以及《Imagine》歌詞。後來這兒被稱為「連儂牆」，成為年輕人追求自由、表達意見的象徵。"},{"pid":"bdaf20e503a8bf1c83fc82130ca9d51dcd571f9d","tid":1394312,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5d241702839b6308ed7389500cc5c833d967eee","tid":1394312,"uid":132686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"我記得好似係有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知有冇記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:22:18.000Z","msg":"有次喺新聞檔案之類既30秒節目提過下連儂牆既來源<br />\n但我肯定佢從來冇稱呼過嗰塊痴滿memo 既牆壁做&ldquo;連儂牆&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebc8862e56f6c2cb746a21a836ed189728ba5f0","tid":1394312,"uid":55936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"無睇好耐喇已經唔知唔理佢做乜9，前線做幾多都被編輯抽起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee8b519b17067b640ab8a79ede7f96454f20046","tid":1394312,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef9436a133e612015f0ef874e970c700e85f6b80","tid":1394312,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"有介紹過出處<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/programmes/internationalnewsfile/5d311374e60383a20ffff061/%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Finternationalnewsfile%2F5d311374e60383a20ffff061%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIETbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=dac024e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/programmes/internationalnewsfile/5d311374e60383a20ffff061/%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86</a><br />\n連儂牆 2019-07-19 11:00 <br />\n<br />\n近期本港多區公眾地方都有市民貼上便利貼，表達反修訂《逃犯條例》等訴求；而在2014年佔領運動期間，亦有人在金鐘夏慤道張貼紙條表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n1980年12月8日，英國樂隊披頭四成員約翰連儂在紐約寓所外被歌迷槍殺身亡，而他與太太1971年創作的《Imagine》，被視為宣揚愛與和平的經典金曲。<br />\n<br />\n1988年，捷克首都布拉格有民眾在修道院廣場的一道牆上，寫上標語及塗鴉，表達對胡薩克共產政權的不滿。部分人在牆上畫有約翰連儂的肖像，以及《Imagine》歌詞。後來這兒被稱為「連儂牆」，成為年輕人追求自由、表達意見的象徵。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"有提出處<br />\n但從來冇正名過香港既連儂牆，一直都叫&ldquo;表達訴求既紙張&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4629aa95e3cb2788cc3d80d71b305b46c6d45802","tid":1394312,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">毫無人格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5d5f9c9be3936b28da3f7b4af432984934cb6839","tid":1394312,"uid":295912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"cctvb<br />\n你唔係仲睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇得多變弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad273547c6506b2113a8ee0996bbf1b7ac11d68","tid":1394312,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d5f9c9be3936b28da3f7b4af432984934cb6839","tid":1394312,"uid":295912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"cctvb<br />\n你唔係仲睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇得多變弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"有時屋企人開黎睇我都冇為意係咩台<br />\n一經發現已經俾我轉返做其他台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e08761bc4eb6695d82c1fb3c92caeedb6cc80e","tid":1394312,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"葵芳光頭人舉槍瞄人都冇影啦, tvb一向剪輯新聞, <br />\n全港得佢最大免費電視牌照, 最多頻道, 想續牌緊係要親政府啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/